body:
These are used as booleans. I would suggest something like:

```cpp
struct {
    bool local{false};
    bool i2p{false};
    bool onion{false};
} networks;
...
if (node.m_is_local) {
    networks.local = true;
}

// if (networks) becomes:
if (networks.local || networks.i2p || networks.onion)
```

